      "span_text": "For example, such items as \"How often do you think of how you can free up more time to work\" (salience) and \"How often do you spend much more time working than initially intended\" (tolerance) from the Bergen Work Addiction Scale [CITATION_1] may have significant residuals' covariance, conceivably attributable to this general involvement factor and different from compulsion/addiction which is assessed by the whole scale .",
